<paragraph id="8BCB36FBFFDFFFA71A88FBE553E6F92B" blockId="3.[151,684,1106,1707]" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE54B0AFFDFFFA71A88FBE55064FBEB" author="LEBIS E." box="[151,302,1106,1131]" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" pagination="25 - 130" refId="ref7210" refString="LEBIS E. 1960. - Helictopleurina, in Faune de Madagascar, XI, Insectes Coleopteres Scarabaeidae. Institut de Recherche scientifique, Tananarive: 25 - 130." type="book chapter" year="1960">Lebis (1960)</bibRefCitation>
regroupe six espèces au sein du « groupe 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71AE4FBC5502EFB0B" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[251,356,1138,1163]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semivirens">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71AE4FBC5502EFB0B" box="[251,356,1138,1163]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">semivirens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
»: 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71B93FBC553E2FB0B" authority="Lebis, 1960" authorityName="Lebis, O. Montreuil" authorityYear="1960" box="[396,680,1138,1163]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aeneoniger">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71B93FBC55357FB0B" box="[396,541,1138,1163]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. aeneoniger</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE54B0AFFDFFFA7183AFBC553E2FB0B" author="LEBIS E." box="[549,680,1138,1163]" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" pagination="25 - 130" refId="ref7210" refString="LEBIS E. 1960. - Helictopleurina, in Faune de Madagascar, XI, Insectes Coleopteres Scarabaeidae. Institut de Recherche scientifique, Tananarive: 25 - 130." type="book chapter" year="1960">Lebis, 1960</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71A88FB2550FFFB2B" authority="d'Orbigny, 1915" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[151,437,1170,1195]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="niger">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71A88FB2551BAFB2B" box="[151,240,1170,1195]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. niger</emphasis>
d’Orbigny, 1915
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71BDEFB25504DFB4B" authority="d'Orbigny, 1915" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semivirens">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71BDEFB25531BFB2B" box="[449,593,1170,1195]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. semivirens</emphasis>
d’Orbigny, 1915
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71B0EFB05531CFB4B" authority="d'Orbigny, 1915" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[273,598,1202,1227]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="seminiger">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71B0EFB0550DFFB4B" box="[273,405,1202,1227]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. seminiger</emphasis>
d’Orbigny, 1915
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA7187FFB05502FFB6B" authority="Lebis, 1960" authorityName="Lebis" authorityYear="1960" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gibbicollis">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA7187FFB055194FB6B" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. gibbicollis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE54B0AFFDFFFA71AFAFB65502FFB6B" author="LEBIS E." box="[229,357,1234,1259]" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" pagination="25 - 130" refId="ref7210" refString="LEBIS E. 1960. - Helictopleurina, in Faune de Madagascar, XI, Insectes Coleopteres Scarabaeidae. Institut de Recherche scientifique, Tananarive: 25 - 130." type="book chapter" year="1960">Lebis, 1960</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71B96FB6553E2FB6B" authority="d'Orbigny, 1915" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[393,680,1234,1259]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71B96FB6550AFFB6B" box="[393,485,1234,1259]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. tristis</emphasis>
d’Orbigny, 1915
</taxonomicName>
. P a u l i a n &amp; C a m b e f o r t (1 9 9 1) y a j o u t e r o n t 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71A88FAA55044FAAB" authorityName="Paulian &amp; Cambefort" authorityYear="1991" box="[151,270,1298,1323]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="steineri">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71A88FAA55044FAAB" box="[151,270,1298,1323]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. steineri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Ces espèces partageraient, d’après Lebis, un pronotum lisse, très finement ponctué, une absence de carène transversale à la base du pygidium et le « huitième interstrie seulement deux fois plus large que le septième dans son tiers antérieur », en opposition aux espèces du « groupe 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71AE3FA6550EFFA6B" authorityName="Olivier" authorityYear="1789" box="[252,421,1490,1515]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Scarabaeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadripunctatus">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71AE3FA6550EFFA6B" box="[252,421,1490,1515]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">quadripunctatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
». 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71BD8FA65536EFA6B" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[455,548,1490,1515]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71BD8FA65536EFA6B" box="[455,548,1490,1515]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71856FA655187F98B" authorityName="Lebis" authorityYear="1960" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gibbicollis">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71856FA655187F98B" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. gibbicollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ont le huitième interstrie très fortement élargi dans son tiers antérieur, ce qui les place, à mon avis, dans le « groupe 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71BD4F9855332F9CB" authorityName="Olivier" authorityYear="1789" box="[459,632,1586,1611]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Scarabaeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadripunctatus">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71BD4F9855332F9CB" box="[459,632,1586,1611]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">quadripunctatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
». Il est à noter que Lebis utilise d’emblée ce même caractère pour isoler 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71B8FF9C550BCF90B" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[400,502,1650,1675]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71B8FF9C550BCF90B" box="[400,502,1650,1675]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
dans sa clé des espèces du « groupe 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71B93F925534AF92B" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[396,512,1682,1707]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semivirens">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71B93F925534AF92B" box="[396,512,1682,1707]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">semivirens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
». 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D78FFDFFFA71839F92553C7F92B" authorityName="d'Orbigny" authorityYear="1915" box="[550,653,1682,1707]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Helictopleurus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis id="B900EAE9FFDFFFA71839F92553C7F92B" box="[550,653,1682,1707]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="126">H. tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et
</paragraph>
